### 알림 디바이스 등록
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/notification-devices
Content-Type: application/json
X-USER-ID: 1

{
  "agentId": "test-agent-id-456",
  "osType": "IOS",
  "deviceName": "iPhone 15 Pro",
  "isActive": true
}

### 알림 활성화 상태 수정 (활성화)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/v1/notification-devices/1/activation
Content-Type: application/json
X-USER-ID: 1

{
  "isActive": true
}

### 알림 활성화 상태 수정 (비활성화)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/v1/notification-devices/1/activation
Content-Type: application/json
X-USER-ID: 1

{
  "isActive": false
}
